### Variables
@API_URL = http://localhost:3000
@TOKEN = your_jwt_token_here


### 1. Create Client
POST {{API_URL}}/api/admin/clients
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "name": "Cliente Test",
  "description": "Descripci√≥n del cliente de prueba",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/logo.png",
  "basicUsername": "testclient",
  "basicPassword": "password123"
}


### 2. Get All Clients (with pagination)
GET {{API_URL}}/api/admin/clients?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### 3. Get All Clients (without pagination)
GET {{API_URL}}/api/admin/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### 4. Get Client by ID
@CLIENT_ID = your_client_id_here
GET {{API_URL}}/api/admin/clients/{{CLIENT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### 5. Reset Client Basic Auth
PATCH {{API_URL}}/api/admin/clients/{{CLIENT_ID}}/reset-basic
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


